Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是大阪的天使迷寄給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.46,0:00:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關西大賽的總決賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.66,0:00:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關西大賽的錄影帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N可以看到王二郎的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的下一個對手就是維札特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個天使好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去年也晉級了全國大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.77,0:00:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維札特明明什麼也沒有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是維札特的絕招\N魔法防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.81,0:00:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然這麼強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我應該怎麼對付他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠夜空閃耀的小星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.96,0:01:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必還無人發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.66,0:01:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它毫不氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.27,0:01:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然如此閃爍光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.80,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎跟我有點相像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.94,0:01:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在擠滿人群的街頭徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已不明白什麼才是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力尋找自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.96,0:01:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要敞開胸懷去接收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.66,0:01:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會明白心靈的悸動\NI wanna get it
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.57,0:02:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢想就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.61,0:02:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時  就在你身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.41,0:02:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此渺小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少是一個開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信遲早會發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世上獨一無二的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要堅定信心就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.03,0:02:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前途在望  做我唯一的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然的兩人獨處\N秘密的雙重約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是王二郎在的話\N就可以叫他來幫忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你整天使喚他\N他也太可憐了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都已經上高中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也已經到了\N想跟女生約會的年紀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了…高中畢業之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不用約什麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一被壞女人騙了那還得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這年頭連國中生\N都已經有女朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他自己一直到高中\N都交不到女朋友啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.14,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎有這樣的變態哥哥\N真是太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽見了，尾形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個外星怪物從哪弄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要懲罰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好好體驗一下再向我報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天八點見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣在公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是虎太郎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.37,0:03:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去澡堂，結果不小心\N把人家的鞋子穿回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種鞋子，怎麼可能會穿錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎他最近好像怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有女生向你表達過愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是珠代嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，你們兩個整天膩在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…因為我們從小就認識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了，什麼兩小無猜那套的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有小學生才會玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟女生玩在一起，那多遜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，珠代也是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.84,0:04:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會弄就別弄，快來看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拳王爭霸戰就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.62,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界拳王賽，妳平常不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代，是世界拳王賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天不是應該快過完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管，我要自己買\N好…來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算要去妳家找妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次去海邊的照片洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一叔叔還是一樣怪裡怪氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在吃大阪煎餅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎你的發音很標準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是關西代表嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在雖然住在神戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是到中學為止\N一直住在東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N阿一叔叔說話跟你不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們不是親兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.32,0:06:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽跟他爸爸都是再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是拖油瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界拳王賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼珠代一定正在看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.97,0:07:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來阿一叔叔和王二郎\N不是親兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該問這種問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糖炒栗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小學的時候\N一天到晚吃這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很愛吃栗子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，最討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得\N我媽媽剛剛再婚的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.62,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對新爸爸還有新哥哥\N一直都是保持距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N新爸爸拼命想跟我拉近關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天\N他買了一包栗子回來給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我最討厭吃糖炒栗子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.37,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻騙他說\N謝謝爸爸，我最愛吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後他天天買栗子給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經假裝說我最愛吃麻花糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我怕外公外婆會覺得失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為怕外公外婆會擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故意說我不想騎腳踏車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.62,0:08:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，電梯突然卡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.76,0:08:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.56,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎的天使\N為什麼叫做維札特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維札特，它的意思是魔法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候還練習唸咒語\N想當巫師呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小光呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光\N這是我以前心愛娃娃的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕外公外婆會寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以放在鄉下代替我陪伴他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個娃娃\N是我很小的時候媽媽送給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想不想見妳媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是也在東京嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，她的工作一直很忙碌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經有祥子陪我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以玩好玩的天使領域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又交了好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.52,0:09:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想見她，畢竟她是我媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓我媽左右為難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你總是對我這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不但陪我練習操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還自願當我的助理，今天也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很好奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.09,0:10:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為\N妳長得很像我的初戀對象吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，只是在想你的初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得她是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見她的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.95,0:10:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才唸小學五年級\N她卻已經二十六歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她完全把我當個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你當小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.92,0:10:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N當時的我根本不可能向她表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果，我只能默默的看著她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.46,0:10:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還是很喜歡\N你說的那個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有正式被拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以到現在\N都沒有辦法徹底死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.11,0:11:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候開始\N我就沒有交過女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.82,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經高中了，竟然沒女朋友\N很遜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得\N你應該鼓起勇氣表白才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你心中的感情\N告訴初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小學時候發生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，你現在還喜歡她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你什麼都不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方當然不可能明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.97,0:11:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也沒有資格說你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.74,0:11:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，王二郎你長得這麼帥\N又這麼溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信一定都會喜歡上你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝妳，美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最早是小兔班的小茜對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎喜歡的女生\N我全部都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳的初戀情人又是誰\N珠代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是虎太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還是我第一次\N跟別人說了這麼多自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我很榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來看看嘛，那邊那個小帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買一個送給可愛的女朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當作今天的約會紀念嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子，也算是在約會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.99,0:13:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看王二郎好像很喜歡妳\N美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有，王二郎都已經上高中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我才剛剛唸國一而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他頂多把我當妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，就買這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳了，美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我玩得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.43,0:13:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，今天讓你聽了我說\N那麼多無聊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.57,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，交情歸交情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的比賽，我可不會讓妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我也會全力以赴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著，我一定會打進決賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萩子，這一次我一定要贏妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.74,0:14:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你隨便說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行\N能讓我分心就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…關於上一次那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在海邊的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人會在這種情況下\N講這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夠倒楣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但被關在這個爛電梯裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不能上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還被男生當面拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我又沒有拒絕妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你心裡喜歡的\N是小咲咲對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.71,0:14:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.78,0:15:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧，我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟那個根本是兩回事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我面前對她臉紅心跳的\N就夠傷人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為\N我從來就沒有把妳當成女生看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.96,0:15:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會這個樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是，我是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.31,0:15:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，反正珠代也還沒有來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代打過電話叫我們先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，虎太郎也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，王二郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萩子，妳說這種話沒有關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，我只是叫你加油而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒叫你贏這場比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是妳，還是妳的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，今天就麻煩妳了，廣美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢\N我看我大概也派不上用場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是哪來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該算哥哥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使領域公式爭霸賽準決賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是準決賽第一場比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東方角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次參加大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就打敗無數強敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.22,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路晉級到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟的新人，鈴原美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是過去兩屆大賽\N都打進最後總決賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜兩次都屈居亞軍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使界貴公子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三原王二郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.58,0:17:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是不知道\N魔法防護罩的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.22,0:17:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過王二郎，我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年王二郎特別強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好連妳都打不過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎的對手也很不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.77,0:17:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，這次最令人好奇的領域\N就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群山環繞的這片綠色草原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這次的舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個讓人想起\N武俠片決鬥場景的舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方到底會使出\N什麼樣的戰鬥招式呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位千萬不要錯過好戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道魔法防護罩\N到底是什麼招術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只好先試試看再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.07,0:18:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預備，天使戰鬥，開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光立刻展開攻勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是維札特\N在千鈞一髮之際躲開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是準決賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場高水準的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，小光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事又不是小咲咲的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡，可以坐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是萩子的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲，妳要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維札特還有魔法防護罩的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.21,0:19:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用給我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為，這等於是間接接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…\N反正你又沒把我當女生看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為妳說了那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確沒有把妳當成女生看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，妳說了那句話之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我多少開始意識到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.88,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果\N就越看越覺得妳是一個女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有辦法\N像以前那樣看妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，妳以後\N不要再用摔角的招式來打我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是\N也不可以共騎一輛腳踏車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.53,0:20:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，也不可以隨隨便便\N闖到我房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.97,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，就算下雨\N也不能合撐一把傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光，衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了，魔法防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.97,0:21:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維扎特在關西大賽\N決賽用過的秘密武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.31,0:21:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用出手就能把對方天使\N彈開的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直太神奇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.65,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小咲咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.89,0:21:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小咲咲，加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，鈴原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小咲咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代，還有虎太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他踢出去，小咲咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個還是趕來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.71,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，戰鬥才剛剛開始而已呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光又站起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎雖然很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我也不會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小咲咲，加…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.47,0:22:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不禁開始習慣依賴你的溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.99,0:23:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歷經無數夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.80,0:23:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於發現最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.00,0:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定不會再遲疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.67,0:23:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的眼中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只看見你一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.17,0:23:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一叔叔\N我想破腦袋還是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法防護罩的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.77,0:23:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不打破那透明防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.57,0:23:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有辦法接近維札特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎為了跟雅典娜決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一次可是卯足了勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.58,0:23:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是，我也想跟她打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.75,0:23:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜，那個白色的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.25,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳就要仔細的觀察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.55,0:23:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維札特，還有妳自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.48,0:23:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回\N機動天使AngeIic Layer
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.09,0:24:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打破魔法障礙，美咲對王二郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.19,0:24:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光，我們一起加油吧
